{"contentType":"application/gliffy+json","version":"1.1","metadata":{"title":"untitled","revision":0,"exportBorder":false},"embeddedResources":{"index":0,"resources":[]},"stage":{"objects":[{"x":694,"y":390,"rotation":0,"id":46,"uid":"com.gliffy.shape.basic.basic_v1.default.text","width":393,"height":42,"lockAspectRatio":false,"lockShape":false,"order":46,"graphic":{"type":"Text","Text":{"tid":null,"valign":"middle","overflow":"none","vposition":"none","hposition":"none","html":"<p style=\"text-align:left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px; font-family: Arial; white-space: pre-wrap; text-decoration: none; line-height: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">分账户模型而论，UTXO账户模型不存在余额的概念，或者说余额就是统计所有的UTXO，UTXO保存在链上；Acount Balance账户模型，一个账户对应一个地址，对应一个余额，同样余额也保存在链上。</span></p>","paddingLeft":2,"paddingRight":2,"paddingBottom":2,"paddingTop":2}},"children":null,"linkMap":[]},{"x":797,"y":277,"rotation":0,"id":42,"uid":"com.gliffy.shape.basic.basic_v1.default.ellipse","width":100,"height":75,"lockAspectRatio":false,"lockShape":false,"order":30,"graphic":{"type":"Shape","Shape":{"tid":"com.gliffy.stencil.ellipse.basic_v1","strokeWidth":2,"strokeColor":"#333333","fillColor":"#FFFFFF","gradient":false,"dropShadow":false,"state":0,"shadowX":0,"shadowY":0,"opacity":1}},"children":[{"x":2,"y":0,"rotation":0,"id":43,"uid":null,"width":96,"height":14,"lockAspectRatio":false,"lockShape":false,"order":"auto","graphic":{"type":"Text","Text":{"tid":null,"valign":"middle","overflow":"none","vposition":"none","hposition":"none","html":"<p style=\"text-align:center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px; font-family: Arial; white-space: pre-wrap; text-decoration: none; line-height: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">余额</span></p>","paddingLeft":2,"paddingRight":2,"paddingBottom":2,"paddingTop":2}},"children":null}],"linkMap":[]},{"x":60,"y":470,"rotation":0,"id":40,"uid":"com.gliffy.shape.basic.basic_v1.default.text","width":560,"height":154,"lockAspectRatio":false,"lockShape":false,"order":28,"graphic":{"type":"Text","Text":{"tid":null,"valign":"middle","overflow":"none","vposition":"none","hposition":"none","html":"<p style=\"text-align:left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px; font-family: Arial; white-space: pre-wrap; text-decoration: none; line-height: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">哈希算法具有以下四种特性：\n</span></p><p style=\"text-align:left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px; font-family: Arial; white-space: pre-wrap; text-decoration: none; line-height: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">1、原像不可逆：公钥不可推导出私钥\n</span></p><p style=\"text-align:left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px; font-family: Arial; white-space: pre-wrap; text-decoration: none; line-height: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">\n</span></p><p style=\"text-align:left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px; font-family: Arial; white-space: pre-wrap; text-decoration: none; line-height: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">2、难题友好性：破解私钥的唯一办法就是暴力猜解\n</span></p><p style=\"text-align:left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px; font-family: Arial; white-space: pre-wrap; text-decoration: none; line-height: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">\n</span></p><p style=\"text-align:left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px; font-family: Arial; white-space: pre-wrap; text-decoration: none; line-height: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">3、发散性：只需要对内容做出极小改动，产生的Hash值将大相径庭\n</span></p><p style=\"text-align:left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px; font-family: Arial; white-space: pre-wrap; text-decoration: none; line-height: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">\n</span></p><p style=\"text-align:left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px; font-family: Arial; white-space: pre-wrap; text-decoration: none; line-height: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">4、抗碰撞性：\n</span></p><p style=\"text-align:left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px; font-family: Arial; white-space: pre-wrap; text-decoration: none; line-height: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">      弱抗碰撞性：当给定某条消息的散列值时，单向散列函数必须确保要找到和该条消息具有相同散列值的另外一条消息是非常困难的。\n</span></p><p style=\"text-align:left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px; font-family: Arial; white-space: pre-wrap; text-decoration: none; line-height: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">      强抗碰撞性：是指要找到散列值相同的两条不同的消息是非常困难的。\n</span></p><p style=\"text-align:left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px; font-family: Arial; white-space: pre-wrap; text-decoration: none; line-height: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"></span></p>","paddingLeft":2,"paddingRight":2,"paddingBottom":2,"paddingTop":2}},"children":null,"linkMap":[]},{"x":60.00000000000006,"y":345,"rotation":0,"id":36,"uid":"com.gliffy.shape.basic.basic_v1.default.text","width":559.9999999999999,"height":84,"lockAspectRatio":false,"lockShape":false,"order":25,"graphic":{"type":"Text","Text":{"tid":null,"valign":"middle","overflow":"none","vposition":"none","hposition":"none","html":"<p style=\"text-align:left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(255, 0, 0); white-space: pre-wrap; text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold; line-height: 14px;\">地址是采用哈希算法算法生成的公钥Hash的一种友好的表现形式。\n</span></p><p style=\"text-align:left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(255, 0, 0); white-space: pre-wrap; text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold; line-height: 14px;\">\n</span></p><p style=\"text-align:left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(255, 0, 0); white-space: pre-wrap; text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold; line-height: 14px;\">不同区块链采用不同的Hash算法，如SHA256、RIPEMD160等等，哈希算法保证了地址的唯一性。\n</span></p><p style=\"text-align:left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(255, 0, 0); white-space: pre-wrap; text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold; line-height: 14px;\">\n</span></p><p style=\"text-align:left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(255, 0, 0); white-space: pre-wrap; text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold; line-height: 14px;\">私钥 推导出 公钥，公钥 推导出 地址，私钥可以产生多个公钥，一把公钥对应一个地址，私钥既代表了用户，地址是公钥（太长）的友好展现形式。\n</span></p><p style=\"text-align:left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(255, 0, 0); white-space: 